    "faq_with_image_6W9cPD": {
      "type": "faq-with-image",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_JNrH7e": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What can I learn from the \"Bespoke Engagement Ring Design\" guide series?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>This complete guide series walks you through the entire custom engagement ring journey. </p><p>You'll find expert articles on crucial topics like diamond selection (both natural and lab-grown), exploring different ring styles and settings, understanding the step-by-step bespoke process, and the importance of ethical sourcing for your materials.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_whVgPH": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "I'm new to lab-grown diamonds. Is there a guide for that?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Yes, our \"Lab-Grown Diamonds\" guide is an expert resource perfect for anyone curious about this modern, ethical option. It explains what lab-grown diamonds are, why they are real diamonds, and the key benefits of choosing one for your engagement ring or fine jewellery, particularly for clients in and around Chichester.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_ChQqBh": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "How do I properly care for my jewellery? Do you have a guide for that?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Our \"Fine Jewellery Care\" guide provides comprehensive, expert advice to keep your treasured pieces safe and sparkling. </p><p>The articles cover the best methods for cleaning different materials like gold, silver, and diamonds, as well as essential tips on proper storage to prevent damage and maintain your heirlooms.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_HLkVVU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What's the difference between your \"Bespoke Jewellery Design\" and \"Jewellery Remodelling\" guides?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Our \"Bespoke Jewellery Design\" guide explores the art of creating a brand-new piece of jewellery from scratch, turning your unique vision into reality. </p><p>In contrast, the \"Jewellery Remodelling\" guide focuses on transforming your existing, perhaps sentimental or outdated, pieces into a beautiful new design you'll love to wear again.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_z6afdq": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What kind of content can I expect to find in \"The Griffin & Co. Journal\"?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>\"The Griffin & Co. Journal\" is our curated collection of expert guidance, insights, and stories illuminating the world of fine jewellery. </p><p>It features all our main guide series—on topics like bespoke design, lab diamonds, repairs, and jewellery care—as well as inspirational customer stories and updates on community giveaways.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
